    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦法院驳回前总理汗无罪释放请求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/pakistan-court-rejects-ex-pm-khan-acquittal-request-in-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦法院驳回了前总理伊姆兰·汗提出的撤销对其执政期间隐瞒出售外国领导人礼品收入的指控的请求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/pakistan-court-rejects-ex-pm-khan-acquittal-request-in-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 07:04:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本计划向低收入家庭发放 192 美元补助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/japan-plans-192-handouts-for-low-income-households-in-package</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社看到的最新计划草案显示，日本首相石破茂政府正计划发放 30,000 日元（192 美元）现金，帮助低收入家庭应对物价上涨，同时充实即将出台的经济一揽子计划的细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/japan-plans-192-handouts-for-low-income-households-in-package</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 07:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯将减少战争中受伤士兵的工资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/russia-to-reduce-payments-for-soldiers-wounded-in-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着入侵成本的不断增加，俄罗斯政府正在减少向乌克兰战争中受伤较轻的士兵支付的赔偿金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/russia-to-reduce-payments-for-soldiers-wounded-in-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 06:42:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非在骚乱后部分重新开放莫桑比克边境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/south-africa-partially-reopens-mozambique-border-after-unrest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于前一天发生抗议活动，南非与莫桑比克的主要边境暂停通行，周四上午，南非开始允许部分边境通行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/south-africa-partially-reopens-mozambique-border-after-unrest</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 06:14:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡领导人希望通过议会投票获得支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/sri-lanka-leader-seeks-to-bolster-power-with-parliamentary-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡举行了该党外来左翼总统获胜以来的首次议会选举，以检验其打击腐败和修改不受欢迎的国际货币基金组织贷款计划的雄心勃勃的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/sri-lanka-leader-seeks-to-bolster-power-with-parliamentary-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国指责中国对电信企业进行大规模网络间谍活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/us-accuses-china-of-broad-and-significant-cyber-spying-effort</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国官员周三在一份声明中表示，中国政府支持的黑客发起了一场“广泛而重大的网络间谍活动”，入侵了多家电信公司，并证实了有关具有重大国家安全影响的网络攻击的更多细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/us-accuses-china-of-broad-and-significant-cyber-spying-effort</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 21:06:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰盟友将在 G20 峰会上敦促中国改善俄朝关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/ukraine-allies-to-push-china-on-russia-north-korea-ties-at-g-20</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，乌克兰盟友将在巴西举行的二十国集团峰会上就朝鲜加大对俄罗斯战争的支持向中国施压。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/ukraine-allies-to-push-china-on-russia-north-korea-ties-at-g-20</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 20:42:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OMV 称俄罗斯天然气供应可能在仲裁中胜诉后停止</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/omv-wins-230-million-award-from-gazprom-on-2022-gas-dispute</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OMV AG 警告称，在与 Gazprom PJSC 的仲裁中，该公司获得了 2.3 亿欧元（2.43 亿美元）的赔偿，此后俄罗斯的天然气供应可能会受到限制，这将提高这家奥地利公司的利润，但可能会终止从克里姆林宫控制的这家公司的采购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/omv-wins-230-million-award-from-gazprom-on-2022-gas-dispute</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 20:22:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>检方寻求禁止勒庞参选法国总统 或将无缘竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/le-pen-risks-missing-presidential-race-as-prosecutors-seek-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国右翼国民联盟党领袖玛丽娜·勒庞面临错过法国下一届总统竞选的风险，此前，贪污案审判结束后，检察官要求立即禁止她五年内参加竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/le-pen-risks-missing-presidential-race-as-prosecutors-seek-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 19:02:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
